msgctxt "sn51.1:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 51 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 51 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. VAR: 1. Cāpālavagga → pāvālavaggo (s1-3)
msgctxt "sn51.1:0.2"
msgid "1. Cāpālavagga "
msgstr "1. At the Cāpāla Shrine "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn51.1:0.3"
msgid "1. Apārasutta "
msgstr "1. From the Near Shore "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.254, sc1
msgctxt "sn51.1:1.1"
msgid "“Cattārome, bhikkhave, iddhipādā bhāvitā bahulīkatā apārā pāraṃ gamanāya saṃvattanti. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, when these four bases of psychic power are developed and cultivated they lead to going from the near shore to the far shore. "

msgctxt "sn51.1:1.2"
msgid "Katame cattāro? "
msgstr "What four? "

msgctxt "sn51.1:1.3"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu chandasamādhippadhānasaṅkhārasamannāgataṃ iddhipādaṃ bhāveti, "
msgstr "It’s when a mendicant develops the basis of psychic power that has immersion due to enthusiasm, and active effort. "

msgctxt "sn51.1:1.4"
msgid "vīriyasamādhippadhānasaṅkhārasamannāgataṃ iddhipādaṃ bhāveti, "
msgstr "They develop the basis of psychic power that has immersion due to energy, and active effort. "

msgctxt "sn51.1:1.5"
msgid "cittasamādhippadhānasaṅkhārasamannāgataṃ iddhipādaṃ bhāveti, "
msgstr "They develop the basis of psychic power that has immersion due to mental development, and active effort. "

msgctxt "sn51.1:1.6"
msgid "vīmaṃsāsamādhippadhānasaṅkhārasamannāgataṃ iddhipādaṃ bhāveti. "
msgstr "They develop the basis of psychic power that has immersion due to inquiry, and active effort. "

msgctxt "sn51.1:1.7"
msgid "Ime kho, bhikkhave, cattāro iddhipādā bhāvitā bahulīkatā apārā pāraṃ gamanāya saṃvattantī”ti. "
msgstr "When these four bases of psychic power are developed and cultivated they lead to going from the near shore to the far shore.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn51.1:1.8"
msgid "Paṭhamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

